The second he woke up in a bed with the laughs of his kids coming from another room, He knew it was the timeline he had been looking for, for so long. Instantly he began to cry silently. He was so happy....Now...he needed to find Argenti...rather...Polnareff..
Polnareff was....fishing?  *Weird, I'm not usually the fishing kind of guy.*
After he had stopped crying he got up and got dressed, he greeted his kids. He made breakfast for them and said he would be back soon. He wanted to go find an old friend of his
"Woah, I caught a big one! Abdul is gonna love this!" *That's it. This is the best universe.*

"Buongiorno, kids!"

"Kids! I want you to meet a close friend of mine! This is Polnareff!" Diavolo called out

They paused their game and came up to greet him
Polnareff laughed. "Greetings!"

"This is Trish and Doppio!" He smiled, patting their heads

"Daddddd no messing up my hair! Its not easy to make it look good." Trish huffed a bit
"I get how you feel, Trish!" He pointed to his hair, still a tall flat top
"Woahhhh! Your hair is like, so cool!!!" She seemed amazed "Do you style it yourself????"
"I usually need a whole bottle of gel!"
"Woah....You sure are dedicated...."
"I've had this style since the 1980s!"

"Woah!!!" Shes impressed

Doppio is impressed too
"Back in those days I fought a vampire." He chuckles

"Oh my friend Giorno is half vampire! Hes a cool dude." 

"Woahhh your friends with a vampire?" Doppio asked Trish
"I might've fought his dad."
"But who knows? Could've been any vampire!"
"Cool....." Trish smiled
"It was a crazy 50 days."

//I didn't notice the message on may 7th
They where in a large beautiful home. Diavolo smiled as he stood there
Trish followed, as she entered as she just squeezed her eyes shut before slowly opening them. To see a large building. It was quite a sight to behold. “Where are we..?”
"Home." He grinned "This is the timeline where I take care of you and Doppio!"
“Its wonderful..I cant believe a place like this ever existed. Its a wonderful home.” She just looked up at the building, stepping forward a bit. She had somewhat of a bittersweet smile on her face.
Polnareff is fishing once more

"Lets go inside then!" He unlocked the door

Doppio was currently chilling on the couch plahing a game when he heard the door unlock "Hi Dad! Hi Trish!!" He smiled
“Oh! Uhm! Hi Doppio..!“ She just smiles and waves as doppio greeted them. To be honest with herself, it felt like a familiar place.

"Do ya wanna play a game with me??? Im playing Mario Kart!!" He hummed

Diavolo smiled
“Sure.” She just had a goofy grin on as she walked over and sat down with doppio. Looking Over at the game. It really did feel like home.

He handed her a controller "This time Im gonna win I can feel it." He chuckled

"Ill make some food for you guys. Any specific you want??"

“Hah, we’ll bet on that.” She just chuckled a bit before looking up at Diavolo. “Not really. Thanks dad.” She really didnt think when she called him dad. It might’ve been normal for this timeline’s trish, but she acted on an impulse.
